    "Evaluation": {
      "text": "Infectious work up\nNot sensitive or specific\nCBC- can show\nanemia\nand\nthrombocytopenia\nLFTs\n- often elevated 3-5x normal\nLumbar puncture\n- resembles aseptic meningitis",
      "subsections": {
        "Diagnostic_labs": {
          "text": "Immunofluorescent assay is the gold standard\nBecomes diagnostic with time.  Rarely positive at onset of illness.\nPCR",
          "tables": []
        }
